<A>__{nomak follows the nurse to a steel door were two security guards await them. both look bored, paying little attention to the monitor which offers a view of the examining room beyond. there is also a small window with safety glass. guard #1 opens the door, following nomak and the nurse inside. guard #2 remains behind, manning the hallway.}
